<Layout title="Angel Baez">
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="/"><p>Angel Baez</p></a>
    </nav>
    <h5><em>vitam impendere vero = to pay his life for the truth</em></h5>
    <h1 class="text-gradient">Developer, entrepreneur and tacos connoisseur</h1>
    <p>
      If you're looking for a developer with an entrepreneurial spirit and
      life-long learning mindset, <mark>you're in the right place</mark>.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
      <a href="mailto:a@baezor.io"><i>Let's talk! ↗</i></a>
      <a href="https://github.com/baezor" target="_blank"><b>Github ↗</b></a>
      <a href="https://twitter.com/baezor" target="_blank"><i>Twitter ↗</i></a>
